 
<p>
The 6 uniformed thugs of Kenly, North Carolina, who are white, all
handed in resignations after the 
<a href="https://boingboing.net/2022/07/29/entire-police-department-quits-after-black-woman-hired-as-city-manager-in-north-carolina.html">town appointed a black woman as city
manager.</a>
